========================

Standard Git Ignore File

========================

--------------------------

1. Dependency Directories

--------------------------

/node_modules
/server/node_modules
/client/node_modules

--------------------------

2. Build / Distribution Files

--------------------------

The compiled JavaScript output (from TypeScript)

/dist
/server/dist

React build output

/client/build
/client/dist
/client/.vite

--------------------------

3. Environment and Configuration

--------------------------

Environment variables (Critical: Do not commit secrets!)

.env
/server/.env
/client/.env
.env.*
.env.local

--------------------------

4. Logs and Cache

--------------------------

npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
*.log
/server/logs
/client/logs

VS Code directory (optional, but often helpful)

.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

--------------------------

5. OS and Editor Files

--------------------------

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db